{"info": {"author": "ni-ning", "author_email": "nining1314@gmail.com", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 3 - Alpha", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 2", "Programming Language :: Python :: 2.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.4", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.5", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7"], "description": "################################\nSend Email for Python\n################################\n\n\n\n**********\n\u529f\u80fd\u7279\u6027\n**********\n\n\u5bf9 Python \u5185\u7f6e\u6a21\u5757 email \u548c smtplib \u7684\u7b80\u5355\u5c01\u88c5\n\n\n********\n\u5b89\u88c5\n********\n\n\u76ee\u524d lightmail \u652f\u6301\u7684 Python \u73af\u5883\u6709 2.7, 3.4, 3.5, 3.6, 3.7\n\n\n\u4e3a\u4e86\u7b80\u5316\u5b89\u88c5\u8fc7\u7a0b\uff0c\u63a8\u8350\u4f7f\u7528 pip \u8fdb\u884c\u5b89\u88c5\n\n.. code-block:: bash\n\n    pip install lightmail\n\n\u5347\u7ea7 lightmail \u5230\u65b0\u7248\u672c::\n\n    pip install -U lightmail\n\n\u5982\u679c\u9700\u8981\u5b89\u88c5 GitHub \u4e0a\u6700\u65b0\u4ee3\u7801::\n\n    pip install https://github.com/ni-ning/lightmail/archive/master.zip\n\n\n\n********\n\u4f7f\u7528\n********\n\n\u9996\u5148\u9700\u8981\u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6 lightmail.cfg, \u6587\u4ef6\u6a21\u677f\u53ef\u53c2\u8003 sample.cfg, \u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6\u67e5\u627e\u8def\u5f84\u4e3a\n\n+ \u5de5\u7a0b\u5f53\u524d\u76ee\u5f55\n+ \u8fd0\u884c\u73af\u5883\u5bb6\u76ee\u5f55\n+ \u914d\u7f6e\u76ee\u5f55 etc\n\n\n\u4f7f\u7528\u6848\u4f8b::\n\n    from lightmail import send_email\n\n    params = {\n        \"to\": \"linda@gmail.com\",\n        \"title\": \"TESTING\",\n        \"content\": \"Hello Python\",\n        \"attach\": [\"@/tmp/test.txt\"]\n    }\n    send_email(**params)\n\n\n\n", "description_content_type": "", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "https://github.com/ni-ning/lightmail", "keywords": "email,smtplib,lightmail", "license": "", "maintainer": "", "maintainer_email": "", "name": "lightmail", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/lightmail/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/lightmail/", "project_urls": {"Homepage": "https://github.com/ni-ning/lightmail"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/lightmail/1.0.0/", "requires_dist": ["six"], "requires_python": "", "summary": "Send Email for Python", "version": "1.0.0", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <div id=\"id1\">\n<h2>\u529f\u80fd\u7279\u6027</h2>\n<p>\u5bf9 Python \u5185\u7f6e\u6a21\u5757 email \u548c smtplib \u7684\u7b80\u5355\u5c01\u88c5</p>\n</div>\n<div id=\"id2\">\n<h2>\u5b89\u88c5</h2>\n<p>\u76ee\u524d lightmail \u652f\u6301\u7684 Python \u73af\u5883\u6709 2.7, 3.4, 3.5, 3.6, 3.7</p>\n<p>\u4e3a\u4e86\u7b80\u5316\u5b89\u88c5\u8fc7\u7a0b\uff0c\u63a8\u8350\u4f7f\u7528 pip \u8fdb\u884c\u5b89\u88c5</p>\n<pre>pip install lightmail\n</pre>\n<p>\u5347\u7ea7 lightmail \u5230\u65b0\u7248\u672c:</p>\n<pre>pip install -U lightmail\n</pre>\n<p>\u5982\u679c\u9700\u8981\u5b89\u88c5 GitHub \u4e0a\u6700\u65b0\u4ee3\u7801:</p>\n<pre>pip install https://github.com/ni-ning/lightmail/archive/master.zip\n</pre>\n</div>\n<div id=\"id3\">\n<h2>\u4f7f\u7528</h2>\n<p>\u9996\u5148\u9700\u8981\u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6 lightmail.cfg, \u6587\u4ef6\u6a21\u677f\u53ef\u53c2\u8003 sample.cfg, \u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6\u67e5\u627e\u8def\u5f84\u4e3a</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u5de5\u7a0b\u5f53\u524d\u76ee\u5f55</li>\n<li>\u8fd0\u884c\u73af\u5883\u5bb6\u76ee\u5f55</li>\n<li>\u914d\u7f6e\u76ee\u5f55 etc</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u4f7f\u7528\u6848\u4f8b:</p>\n<pre>from lightmail import send_email\n\nparams = {\n    \"to\": \"linda@gmail.com\",\n    \"title\": \"TESTING\",\n    \"content\": \"Hello Python\",\n    \"attach\": [\"@/tmp/test.txt\"]\n}\nsend_email(**params)\n</pre>\n</div>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 6211821, "releases": {"0.0.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "1cd83a22958ce5af64c88e6daab69299", "sha256": "745a9067cf3b5435f9348c6e6e1644f2c9fec5cb84930d130f1260c5153cf510"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "lightmail-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "1cd83a22958ce5af64c88e6daab69299", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py3", "requires_python": null, "size": 5103, "upload_time": "2019-11-26T09:45:44", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-11-26T09:45:44.820482Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/02/d0/3f758f1aede849638933e85d308e73ef1016626e48190bfc0c78ba2a5128/lightmail-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "yanked": false}], "1.0.0": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "dc136b042cdd94406f92ef4a00d6ece5", "sha256": "1c24b76d190ff5e05c0b24bcd25e9c1e98624ab8533ff6ab05617b0913a6fea1"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "lightmail-1.0.0-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "dc136b042cdd94406f92ef4a00d6ece5", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py3", "requires_python": null, "size": 5795, "upload_time": "2019-11-28T02:24:28", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-11-28T02:24:28.938787Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/2a/cf/74b521148e68a90fe80f0a5c4085fafa247ccf06050007e980159c52cec7/lightmail-1.0.0-py3-none-any.whl", "yanked": false}]}, "urls": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "dc136b042cdd94406f92ef4a00d6ece5", "sha256": "1c24b76d190ff5e05c0b24bcd25e9c1e98624ab8533ff6ab05617b0913a6fea1"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "lightmail-1.0.0-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "dc136b042cdd94406f92ef4a00d6ece5", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py3", "requires_python": null, "size": 5795, "upload_time": "2019-11-28T02:24:28", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-11-28T02:24:28.938787Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/2a/cf/74b521148e68a90